| 2nd | +2 | Fighting Style, Hunter Tricks                          |  3 | 4 |  d8 |
| 3rd | +2 | Hunting Lodge, Tracker                                 |  3 | 4 |  d8 |
| 4th | +2 | Ability Score Improvement                              |  3 | 4 |  d8 |
| 5th | +3 | Extra Attack, Pathfinding                              |  3 | 4 |  d8 |
