> ## Beast Companion
> *Medium beast, unaligned*
> ___
> - **Armor Class** 13 + PB (natural armor)
> - **Hit Points** 5 + five times your hunter level (the beast has a number of Hit Dice [d8s] equal to your hunter level)
> - **Speed** 40 ft., 50 ft. (Stag or Steed only), 30 ft. (Ape, Crocolisk, Spider only), 5 ft. (Bird only); climb 30 ft. (Bear, Cat, Simian, or Spider only); fly 60 ft. (Bird only); swim 30 ft. (Crocolisk or Snake only)
> ___
> |  STR  |  DEX  |  CON  |  INT  |  WIS  |  CHA  |
> |:-----:|:-----:|:-----:|:-----:|:-----:|:-----:|
> |14 (+2)|14 (+2)|15 (+2)| 8 (-1)|14 (+2)|11 (+0)|
>___
>- **Senses** darkvision 60 ft., passive Perception 12
>- **Languages** understands the languages you speak
>- **Challenge** —
> ___
>
> ***Primal Bond.*** You can add your proficiency bonus to any ability check or saving throw that the beast makes.
>
> ***Endurance Training (Tenacity only).*** The beast gains one additional hit point per hunter level.
>
> ***Predator's Thirst (Ferocity only).*** The beast gains a +1 bonus to damage rolls per five hunter levels.
> 
> ***Trailblazer (Cunning only).*** The beast's movement speeds increase by 5 feet per five hunter levels.
>
> ***Pack Tactics (Raptor or Wolf only).*** The beast has advantage on an attack roll against a creature if at least one of its allies is within 5 feet of the creature and the ally isn't incapacitated.
>
> ***Poisonous Strike (Serpent and Spider only).*** When the beast hits with its bite attack, the target must make a Constitution saving throw against your focus save DC or be poisoned until the end of your next turn.
>
>
> ### Actions
> ***Bite (Bear, Cat, Crocolisk, Raptor, Serpent, Spider, or Wolf).*** *Melee Weapon Attack:* your focus attack modifier to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. *Hit:* 1d8 + 2 + PB piercing damage.
> 
> ***Swipe (Bear, Bird, Boar, Cat, or Raptor).*** *Melee Weapon Attack:* your focus attack modifier to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. *Hit:* 1d6 + 2 + PB slashing damage.
>
> ***Smash (Simian, Stag, or Steed).*** *Melee Weapon Attack:* your focus attack modifier to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. *Hit:* 1d6 + 2 + PB bludgeoning damage damage.
>
> ***Rock (Simian only).*** *Ranged Weapon Attack:* your focus attack modifier to hit, range 25/50 ft., one target. Hit: 1d6 + 2 + PB bludgeoning damage.
>
> ***Web (Recharge 5-6; Spider only).*** *Ranged Weapon Attack:* your focus attack modifier to hit, range 30/60 ft., one creature. *Hit:* The target is restrained by webbing. As an action, the restrained target can make a Strength check, bursting the webbing on a success. The webbing can also be attacked and destroyed (AC 10; hp 5; vulnerability to fire damage; immunity to bludgeoning, poison, and psychic damage).

